name: McDonald's
description: Classic, long-running fast-food chain known for its burgers & fries.
address: McDonald's, 8191 Alderbridge Way, Richmond, BC V6X 3A9

detailed_reviews.review_text: Clean dining environment, fast services, everything was ready in 3 minutes, the staff showed me a big sunshine smile after cally order. Great place to visit if Im craving a solid burger

LIKE IF YOU AGREE! Saw this at the alderbridge way mcdonalds location very nice and helpful. Please no 2 road mcdonalds get this so we dont have to touch the door handle after using washroom and after we wash our hands. It is unsanitary and there are no napkins provided to hold the handle. Thank you .

This is the best McDonalds I have visited. Why? It is very clean and neat. Crew does very good about it. Additionally, in other McDonalds restaurants, we encounter issues like cold drink dispenser malfunction, unstable tables, full trash boxes, etc. So far, we havent seen any of these issues here. They also have a nice sitting area outside. Even though its a bit far from our house, we prefer coming here ehen we crave for a burger :)
Special thanks to Rajvir and his team!! thanks for letting my girl to hold a birthday party in Mcdonald!! They were super helpful and nice!!
A more upscale Cantonese restaurant. The service was beyond reproach. Food was well prepared and had a few interesting dishes I hadnt tried before. Its definitely worth a visit .

Managers are very Friendly, Very helpful, polite and good listener.  They work really hard beyond their limits . I always come in here and enjoy my meal with my family members and friends. Love this place they do have meeting room nice seating area comfortable chairs . Even have patio that we can sit and enjoy .Kids love this place always have balloons and drawings  that we can make kids busy .
I like the seating area, lots of seats, tables look clean, it feels like an oasis where you can just flop down some food and rest.
McD all over the World always the same good quality whether in my home country Indonesia or Canada always the best for Breakfast
Very busy ,  trying out pumpkin latte. Pretty good Parking: Not a lot but high turnover Food : 5/5 |
Busy location, service still pretty quick. Tons and tons of seating space, used to be play area
Their sundae is the best. The texture of their ice cream is firm and always cold enough.

We had fillet o fish. It was amazing! I had the thick Choc smoothie to go with it. I loved the milkshake, so creamy, thick and delicious! Had large fries with it. They have a drive thru as well. Was pretty busy, lots of movement, and service was good. They have lots of parking as well.

went around 315 to 330. whoever was manager / expediter needs a raise. my order which had extra pickles written on the receipt had instead no pickles.  no problem. mistakes happen.  I was impressed with the guy at the desk who immediately apologized and asked the back to make me a new one. it took them forever to give it to me, but when he checked in on me again and discovered I still hadnt gotten the second burger he offered me something (I asked for a iced coffee)  and made it himself. the burger was ok, but this guy is going places.  Id hire this supervisor in a heartbeat.    he is pretty young too.
No doubt I love McDonald s but customer service makes big difference. I must say Tim always serves with big smile   and it makes me wanna to go to this location. He got great sense of humour
<<<NIGHT SHIFT>>> Best McDonald s I ve ever since in like 15 years. Don t waste your time going to the other god awful locations in Richmond. (Looking at you 2rd) Really great stuff.

Came here for the airconditioning and was not disappointed. Cool and fresh, my day improved immediately. Had the big mac and it was typical - dry, processed and no texture. But hey i got ac out of it. Plus they close at 12 midnight!!!

We have visited quite often to this location since I was attending PG. Fast service and friendly servants. Have to wait a little bit longer since lunch hour is the peak time and no parking spaces as well.
Tim is the best worker they have!!! So friendly and accommodating

Very good service. There was one guy whose name was I think Ansh something. He was very nice and polite and satisfied me. He never told me to park my otherwise this drive thru is park thru. He was very quick also. And literally made lots of coffees in one minute. Was really satisfied with the service, which I am getting daily.

Had a fantastic time with one of the managers Christopher, my friend was given very cold fries in which he remade them for her and even brought it to our table. 10/10 for customer service, definitely turned around a soon to be bad experience.

Very good restaurant. A good place to go and have a breakfast, lunch, dinner or just for a quickly snack. Ambient good with a big space divided on 4 rooms. There also a big space in park-lot for your car: With very attention employees and with a fast service on almost times. The drive-true is opened 24 hrs/day.

The evening crew here is very good! The service was super fast and the team was so friendly! They really went above and beyond for us. They ran out to our car to make sure they fixed a mistake (they forgot cheese on my burger) Big thanks!
Nuggets never fail.

I think its standard at McDonalds for all those ordering machines to get stuck and not spit out a receipt so Im not going to hold that against them... The manager was really helpful when I told him of the problem and the order was ready within 3 minutes or less. We went around noon and it was that crowded. The place is fairly clean and organized. Helpful and friendly staff.

Respect to the men working the graveyard shift at the drive thru. Always happy to be served by him. There is that human touch in the conversation :D Other than the world famous fries but that kind of customer service is what makes this review a 5 star instead of a 4.

Its McDonalds, so you already know how it goes. Food is usually the same from place to place. This location however, I do give five stars simply because they rarely get my orders wrong, the food is always fresh (and we all know when our fries are fresh), and the service is fast and friendly. Good job, keep up the good work!

8191 Alderbridge, I used to drop by for my morning coffee regularly but have not visited the site for sometime. This morning I happen to drop by around 6.45 am and saw the familiar face of Tim. Well, I must say he has been there for a very long time and still serve the customers the right way. I admire the dedication in customer service even at the end of a Night Shift I wish Mac.Donalds could recognize such people for their service & dedication.
Many parking spots, fresh fries are quick, staffs are usually friendly.

One of my favorite McDonalds in Richmond. The seating is amazing, a fun place to visit with your family or friends. The service and cleanliness is exceptional. I highly recommend this location. The drive thru service is great.

McDonalds has kinda changed up there marketing scheme abit. Good deals if you use the app and pick it up. Either drive thru, curbside, or front counter. Saves quite abit actully. Friendly quick. And got my order 100% correct on this occasion.  I recommend.
amazing service. I asked them to redo a mccrispy because it looked a lil different and they did it - no questions asked!
Always get fantastic, friendly and fast service here. The morning drive thru crew are my favorite, as they know me and ask me about my day when I swing by for a coffee. I look forward to that.
Good timings open all night
Well maintained old McDonalds. Fast service. Cool conveyor belt system for the drive through in the kitchen. Kid-friendliness: Playplace.
Best McDonald s hashbrown I ve ever had. Cool building as well. Kinda weird drive thru though!

Professional service and friendly staff food was very tasty and delicious yummy and freshly cooked Thank you! Parking: Plenty of parking available Kid-friendliness: Food for my son Wheelchair accessibility: They do have it

This is a great and convenient McDonalds location in central Richmond, but be warned of potential looooong drive-thru line-ups on weekday mornings! Its a busy place! The dining area within the restaurant is very spacious.

I just need to make clear that this was the only McDonalds location that made my single order of a McDouble with TLC. It honestly looked and tasted like perfection. For that, I will always be coming back here. And to whoever made that burger, you have earned mad respect.
The staff are friendly,but it seems they always make some mistakes preparing your orders.
They recently renovated. Really spacious location now. But they didnt have highchairs for toddlers! Food great as usual!

I had such an amazing experience at this Mcdonald :D Najai was simply FANTASTIC. I came to mcdonald wanting to pick up some fries, donuts and some toys. Najai took the time to help me find toys and the staff here are super friendly. Would definitely come back to this Mcdonald again !!
This is one of the cleanest restaurnant i ever saw, staff is really friendly.
Nice clean McDonalds Always good service Food
Clean restaurant, crew are always friendly and helpful. I love their smiles, makes me comfortable and happy to go there. Food is also nice and fresh!
Best Mcdonalds in the area. Drive through is usually packed, but seating is abundant within the diner. They have good service in the case of ordering by machine, pretty clean and upscale Mcdonalds.

Convenient location and very nice and simple interior. Plenty of parking. Only issue is that when you leave, you can only turn right towards North, which could be a bit of a detour if you want to go towards the Lansdowne direction.
i asked for a happy meal toy and the worker said they dont have it. luckily, manager EJ was listening in and told me they did have it. good job guys!
So nice customer service even tho It was quite busy.
Great costumer service via drive thru!
Super friendly staff and really fresh food.
Very pleasant staff, food was good, and premises were very clean.
Pretty good, it was clean. The ice cream machine  was up and running so I was happy.
One of their larger venue. Plenty of seats. Also a drive thru. Kids play area... Close to Canada line, 5 minutes walk to Lansdowne Station.

Only this location n the one in no 3 rd n near grand view ave location are the truly fresh n good Tasteful food in All Richmond Locations (one location I experienced the meat wasnt  even cook ! But When I find out l was home  Already)!
Clean, roomy and airy.
Nice and fast service
Mc Donalds has a good atmosphere, love the food of course. Pretty fast in terms of time from purchasing to start eating.
CAN I GET A SIMPSONS SUPREME HAPPY MEAL PLEASE? I WILL TAKE DOUBLE THE TOYS, ASWELL AS SUPERSIZE MY FRIES. (r)(c)
the best Mcdonald in the area
Food and drinks are always fresh and hot.
Very good
CHICKEN BIG MAC. What else needs to be said. 2023 changed the world forever. Food : 5/5
Surprised at this location. Always always drive by but never stopped. Service was great, place was clean.
It just a McDonald s. Just a friendly reminder that the Drive Thru is tricky.
Usual great coffee and service! Good location across from the mall! Quick little drive through in the back!
Excellent service by Aman. I have been to many Mc Donalds but the customer service provided by this girl was outstanding.
Consistent and inexpensive. Always clean, and the staff are friendly and helpful.
Very delicious food and authentic! Portions are also decent for the price. Would come back
Clean place, nice fast food restaurant
Nice clean place. They never have any napkins out, you always have to ask for them and they only give you 2
Fries was hot... but it was 12:30pm.... overall got what I expected
Clean,  spacious,  newly furnished,  and most importantly,  the manager is extremely helpful (I was a visitor from overseas).
Fast service, hygienic food, especially love the coffee
Very good, but also somewhat expensive
Its right across where I work. Very good price with coupon. Summer drink is great price.
Always good to visit McDonalds, and even more now that they improved their locations.
Clean place and hardworking people.  Food is consistent with McDonald s standards.
Great place to grab a bite while waiting for your buyer/seller from Craigslist to show up!
The services waz quick & great McDonalds da only place i go to for fastfoods
Efficient and fast tasty food lots of parking available
Great location. Very well maintained. Staff is friendly and very efficient.
Hi there mama I loved the picture you sent me. I love you so very much.
Love the new donuts
Very clean and quick service.
They are friendly.  Fast and efficient service.  Good location
It was ok here ...... Customer service is not at all appreciable......
coffee is good and you can choose different types of food
Tradition in fast food. Clean, tasty, cheap and free wifi
Clean and quick. Good place to have a cup of coffee.
Nice staff and good service.
Most McDonalds are the same. Some are in very ghetto places.
A good place to kill time, we should find something meaningful in our life...
Prime location and good parking space
Best service especially at the drive thru
Convenience location, fast service. Five star
The passion fruit smoothy was expectacular!
Probably the best McDonalds in Richmond, good seating and enough parking
Prices are ok. Food is ok. Perfect for late night food with friends.
Its what you expect but it feels nice and clean
One of the better McDonalds Ive been to.

name: McDonald's
description: Classic, long-running fast-food chain known for its burgers & fries.
address: McDonald's, 9251 Alderbridge Way, Richmond, BC V6X 0N1

detailed_reviews.review_text: Thanks to Megan, an a employee there. I was struggling at the kiosk with my account code and she help me through it. She said she worked there and was getting off her shift. She was so nice to me and wanted to help me. I am very grateful that she help me out. I want to give her great review on how she help a customer who was struggling. Thank you again Megan.
One can expect a good customer service experience. Staff working here are so polite and addresses customers timely even during busy hours.

This Mcdonalds is my go to. Whenever i go there, its very clean. The staff is very friendly. One Indian girl Sukhraj  took my order, she was very polite and even offered my kids balloons and coloring sheets. Thank you soo much for going above and beyond for excellent service.

Walmart mcdonalds is one of the best restaurant. Even if there is staff shortage they always try their 100% to serve customers as quickly as possible with accuracy. Their staff is very polite. I saw if someone has issue with their mobile order or they don t know how to order through their phone, their staff always try to help customers and solve their issue. Indian staff is also very nice. They work very hard to make customers happy with serving accurate and fresh food. So nothing bad about this restaurant. Excellent service.

Next to the McDonalds in Quesnel this is the only other location that still makes good food. This is the first time in years Ive got a fresh made and hot McDonalds meal on the coast. Also sending props to the guy working right now for banging out multiple breakfasts without breaking a sweat. Hes so polite and is doing a great job!

Food is good and the Service so fast and affordable we always buy at McDonalds after my graveyard shift and we buy breakfast because no time for me to cook. Kid-friendliness: Yes they allowed children at the store to eat and have fun and they toys for kids when u buy kids Meal.
Its  a nice little  Macdonald  location.

I visited this mcdonalds just last sunday. Although it s small but it was very clean. The staff is very friendly. One girl  Simran  helped me with the mobile ordering. She was very patient  because my internet was very slow and it was taking longer for processing. I was happy with the service.

Walmart Mcdonalds is one of my favourite restaurant. I have really good experience with this McDonald. This is one of the cleanest McDonald in Richmond. Moreover, I like the Quick and friendly service. I would recommend to customers come here and try the fresh food. Excellent service!.

After a long day of shopping this is a great place to unwind and have a quick bite. The customer service is great the staff are friendly and nice and the food are always hot. What best is they have free WIFI!! Definitely gonna recommend.
sometimes the Mcdonald app have special offer for this shop
Great mcdonalds. Not usually too busy. Washroom available.
Very comfortable atmospher..
Easy and quick meal for a person whos in hurry.
This is a very small mcDonald in richmond, they only have less 3 staffs . the service is very Efficience and warmful. the products are upto good Quality and quantity.

A well known Vietnam cuisine in downtown Vancouver. Their drinks and milk shake are use the fresh fruits. Their dessert have lots variety and most of them cant find at other Vietnam restaurant, must try.
$1.29 + tax deal Pick me up treat for the summer :)
I have always had great service and the workers are always nice and work a good speed I enjoy coming here
Mychaela (I believe that s how her name was spelt) is an absolute ROCKSTAR. She was very kind even at the end of her shift. She deserves a big raise!!
Great McDonals for just pick up the food its inside a walmart and its super small
The evening manager during weekends is very nice. She s very polite, nice and make drinks very fast. She treats the customers very well. Great Job
Good service friendly staff and clean.
I was very impressed with how clean and well run this McDonalds was all I seen was two guys running the place and they were doing an excellent job, fast and took pride in there jobs,
Small Mcdonalds store right below Walmart. Very convenient after grocery shopping. Crew were friendly and food was very fresh
It was good, they are fast
Not enough crew food service slow.
This restaurant is very good for snacks and all fast food meals. The employees are polite and with good costumer service. I really recommend this place.
Very fast ,friendly and helpful with MCDONALDS APP.
Most convenient way to fill up your stomach.
Very awesome yummy drinks thanks take care McDonalds
Get what you pay for, every time, quick and convenient, breakfast on the run.
Nice
Always there and nearby when you need a quick snack
Great stop after groceries
I had a great experienced every weekend in the morning team
good deal for Happy Meal
Enjoyed the great service and employee hospitality.
Nice and clean and friendly staff
THEY GAVE ME A MEDIUM, AND I ORDERED A SMALL
